{"tid":1242292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"與美斯合作的九位國家隊教練 都未能成功...","createTime":"2019-06-19T04:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:14:23.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3e6b7d41d19700eb094852a4244cebf775e9f3","tid":1242292,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"據《馬卡報》的統計，自從美斯（L.Messi）亮相阿根廷國家隊之後，在過去14年里合作了9名教練，但都沒能取得成功。<br />\n  這9名教練分別是：比格文（2006-2008）、巴斯利（2008-2010）、馬勒當拿（2010-2011）、巴迪高斯塔（2011-2014）、薩維利亞（2014-2016）、馬天奴（2016-2017）、巴烏薩（2017-2018）、桑保利（2018）以及現在的斯卡洛尼。<br />\n  阿根廷在14年經歷了9名教練，而同期時間烏拉圭只有1名，那就是塔巴雷斯。在2006年上任之後，他一直執教烏拉圭，率隊取得2010年世界盃第四名、2011年美洲盃冠軍。"},{"pid":"a5a1cf7c78e82a0012446924c010540c0c04549e","tid":1242292,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"9條磨碌都冇個識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比d咁嘅嘢我哋小花真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#華維迪OUT"},{"pid":"151c2d7f7dca1ddead20d0dc263fcf4c2ac3a760","tid":1242292,"uid":12980,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:25:57.000Z","msg":"14年入到決賽算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477f4a779c1db0cacf931af1af34a91d31a7cd36","tid":1242292,"uid":12651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:14:23.000Z","msg":"C朗教就得"}]}